                M110,210 h16 v2.5 h-13 v5 h11 v2.5 h-11 v5.5 h13 v2.5 h-16 v-18 Z
                M130,210 h3.5 l8,11.5 v-11.5 h3.5 v18 h-3.5 l-8,-11.5 v11.5 h-3.5 v-18 Z
